# Attendance Web プロジェクト — AI Agent Instructions
# Attendance Web Project — AI Agent Instructions

> **Primary language / 主言語**: 日本語 (Japanese) — all project documents, UI copy, comments, and commit messages.
> **Secondary language / 副言語**: English — every document includes an English section or translation block.
> **Chat response language / チャット応答言語**: **English only** — AI assistant replies in English in chat; code comments and commits remain Japanese.
>
> このファイルは AI アシスタント（Claude / Cursor / Copilot / Windsurf / Gemini など）が **作業前に必ず読む** べき指示書です。
> Copy this file to the project root as `.cursorrules` / `CLAUDE.md` / `.github/copilot-instructions.md` / `GEMINI.md` as needed.

