## 業務ドメインの前提 | Business Domain

**English:**

| Domain | Rule |
|--------|------|
| Request types | Leave, Late, Early leave, Out-of-office |
| Leave dates | Full day / AM half / PM half, or date From–To |
| Time-based requests | Single date + time From–To |
| Processing (optional) | Paid leave (days/half-days/hours) or schedule change |
| Approval | Section Head → HR; rejection reason required |
| Paid leave | Self-view balance; admin views all; warn 2 months before year-end if < 5 days taken |
| Cancel/edit | Allowed before approval; restricted after |

**日本語:**

| ドメイン | ルール |
|---------|--------|
| 申請種別 | 休暇・遅刻・早退・外出 |
| 休暇日付 | 1日 / 午前休 / 午後休、または From–To |
| 時刻系申請 | 単日 + 時刻 From–To |
| 処理方法（任意） | 有給（日数/0.5日/時間）または時間変更 |
| 承認 | 所属上長 → 人事；却下理由必須 |
| 有給 | 自己確認；admin 全員確認；5日未満は2か月前警告 |
| 取消・変更 | 承認前可；承認後は制限 |

詳細: `memory/constitution.md` の「ドメイン仕様」

