## 主要パス | Key Paths

```
src/
  app/(dashboard)/          # Dashboard pages / ダッシュボード
  app/(auth)/               # Login / ログイン
  actions/                  # Server Actions
  components/               # React components
  lib/
    supabase/               # Supabase clients + middleware
    validations/            # Zod schemas
    auth/permissions.ts     # Role helpers
    pdf/                    # PDF generation + upload
    teams/webhook.ts        # MS Teams Adaptive Cards
  messages/ja.json          # Primary i18n
  messages/en.json          # Secondary i18n
supabase/migrations/        # SQL migrations (ordered)
memory/constitution.md      # Development constitution (canonical)
docs/onboarding/            # Onboarding docs (bilingual)
specs/                      # Spec-driven docs (bilingual)
```

